wiki.content:
This song was influenced by Tyler interviewing Nas for XXL Magazine. In the intro and outro of the song you hear Nas reflecting on being a crack dealer and the impact that drug has had on the world. Tyler wrote that song with that in mind, trying to put himself in that perspective.
